#  Deploy Azure Storage Account using ARM Template

This project demonstrates how to deploy an Azure Storage Account using Azure Resource Manager (ARM) templates via Azure CLI.

---

## ðŸ›  Tools Used

- Azure CLI
- Visual Studio Code
- ARM Templates
- Azure Portal

